  <section class="bb-section" id="history">
    <div class="bb-eyebrow">The history of the pain</div>
    <h2 class="bb-h2">Four completed cycles, four brutal drawdowns</h2>
    <p class="bb-lead">Bitcoin has had five bear markets: four are complete, and the current one is the fifth, still unresolved. Every completed cycle has ended in a fall of at least three-quarters from its peak, and every one of those falls was, in hindsight, followed by a new all-time high. Both halves are in the table.</p>

